                  <th class="text-left p-3 border-b">CoinGate</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-b">Self-Hosted</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td><td class="p-3 border-b">❌</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-b">USDT Support</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅ (ERC-20, TRC-20, BEP-20)</td><td class="p-3 border-b">❌</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-b">100+ Chains</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td><td class="p-3 border-b">❌ Bitcoin only</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-b">Zero Platform Fees</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td><td class="p-3 border-b">❌ 1%+</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-b">Deposit/Withdraw</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td><td class="p-3 border-b">❌</td><td class="p-3 border-b">❌</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-b">MistTrack Risk Control</td><td class="p-3 border-b">✅</td><td class="p-3 border-b">❌</td><td class="p-3 border-b">❌</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-b">Deploy Time</td><td class="p-3 border-b">3 minutes</td><td class="p-3 border-b">30+ minutes</td><td class="p-3 border-b">N/A (hosted)</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Conclusion</h2>
          <p>
            Accepting USDT payments doesn't have to mean giving up control or paying high fees. A self-hosted payment gateway like Xcash gives you the best of both worlds: your customers can pay with USDT, while you keep full custody of your private keys and pay zero platform fees.
          </p>
          <p>
            Ready to get started? Deploy Xcash in 3 minutes:
          </p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code>git clone https://github.com/xca-sh/xcash.git
cd xcash && ./scripts/init_env.sh && docker compose up -d</code></pre>
          <p>
            Or visit <a href="https://xca.sh" class="text-primary hover:underline">xca.sh</a> for the cloud-hosted version.
          </p>

        </div>
      </article>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
